String.name: Dueling Scar
String.tooltip: Adds a stack of <font color = '#F9B600'>Dueling Scar</font> after successfully hitting target with <font color = '#F9B600'>Rain of Blows</font> while <font color = '#F9B600'>Defensive Stance</font> is active. Targets with 7 stacks of <font color = '#F9B600'>Dueling Scar</font> are stunned and their Endurance decreases by 9%. Boss monsters are not stunned and Endurance decreases by 1.5%.

String.name: Rapid Strike
String.tooltip: Speeds casting of <font color = '#F9B600'>Rain of Blows</font> by 15% and and doubles the chance to crit while <font color = '#F9B600'>Assault Stance</font> is active. <font color = '#F9B600'>Rain of Blows</font> will no longer reduce damage.

String.name: Wound
String.tooltip: Applies a stack of [Wound] to an enemy player on a successful hit. 7 stacks of [Wound] causes Bleeding, which decreases HP over time and increases damage taken by 9%.

String.name: Spirit of Iron
String.tooltip: Adds Frontal Defense to <font color = '#F9B600'>Rain of Blows</font>, <font color = '#F9B600'>Blade Draw</font>, <font color = '#F9B600'>Scythe</font>, and <font color = '#F9B600'>Aerial Scythe</font> while Defensive Stance is active. However, reduces the damage of these skills by 20% and does not add Frontal Defense in PvP.

String.name: Bellicosity
String.tooltip: Increases duration of <font color = '#F9B600'>Deadly Gamble</font> by 20% while <font color = '#F9B600'>Assault Stance</font> is active. Also increases skill damage to monsters by 5% if Deadly Gamble II is active.

String.name: Encouraging Shout
String.tooltip: <font color = '#F9B600'>Deadly Gamble</font> boosts damage to players by 8% for allies within 6m.

String.name: Defense Tactics
String.tooltip: Increases the window to trigger Perfect Defense by 0.2 sec, and doubles the reflected damage from <font color = '#F9B600'>Retribution Shield</font> passive skill.

String.name: Light Shield
String.tooltip: Decreases required RE by 3 and increases Movement Speed by 40 while holding <font color = '#F9B600'>Stand Fast</font>.

String.name: Retribution
String.tooltip: Increases damage of the next [Shield Counter] by 30% when used within 5 seconds after triggering Perfect Defense.

String.name: March
String.tooltip: Increases PvP damage by 30%, but you take 30% more PvP damage while skill is in effect.

String.name: Strenuous
String.tooltip: Increases caster's effect duration by 25%.

String.name: Change of Strategy
String.tooltip: Increases skill effects by 10%, but no longer affects allies. (Does not stack with another lancer's <font color = '#F9B600'>Adrenaline Rush</font> bonuses.)

String.name: Rebirth
String.tooltip: Recovers an additional 35,000 HP.

String.name: Mental Strength
String.tooltip: Immune to knockdown and stagger. Greatly increases resistance to weakening effects.

String.name: Insight
String.tooltip: Removes all harmful effects, and you become invincible for 1 second. Does not apply Tenacity.

String.name: Balance Factor
String.tooltip: All attacks are considered to be attacks from behind while the effect is active. Overhand Strike decreases Endurance by 9% on a successful hit. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Focus
String.tooltip: Increases duration by 25% and damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Overhand Strike</font> by 10%.

String.name: Armed
String.tooltip: Reduces damage from ranged attacks by 30% and increases Movement Speed in combat by 20.

String.name: Velocity
String.tooltip: Increases Attack Speed and range by 20%.

String.name: Bleeding
String.tooltip: Recovers 3% of your max HP on a successful hit and decreases the target’s Endurance by 5%. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Damage Enhancement
String.tooltip: Increases skill damage by 200%.

String.name: Mock
String.tooltip: Increases damage dealt to monsters within 10m by 3% for 10 seconds. In PvP, increases damage dealt to players by 9%.

String.name: Outrage
String.tooltip: Applies <font color = '#F9B600'>Fiery Rage VI</font> and <font color = '#F9B600'>Flurry of Blows II</font> effects simultaneously.

String.name: Charisma
String.tooltip: Increases PvP damage dealt by 20%, but you take 10% more PvP damage.

String.name: Glacial Explosion
String.tooltip: Cancels the damage over time effect and instantly deals maximum damage to the area.

String.name: Cold Wave
String.tooltip: Decreases a monster’s Endurance by 3% to 9% for 20 seconds after a successful hit. Stacking Hail Storm 4 times stuns the target for 3 sec. Stun effect will only occur once every 15 seconds. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Frostbite
String.tooltip: Doubles the maximum possible stacks of a Movement Speed decrease effect.

String.name: Mysterious
String.tooltip: Grants all element types and increases skill effect duration by 20%.

String.name: Managame
String.tooltip: Replenishes MP of allies within 30m by 20% for 5 seconds and decreases MP of enemies within 30m by 20% for 5 seconds.

String.name: Inner Peace
String.tooltip: Activates a barrier that absorbs 40,000 damage for 5 seconds and provides resistance to stuns while active.

String.name: Deep Cut
String.tooltip: Reduces the effect of healing skills on an enemy player by 30% for 10 seconds after a successful hit.

String.name: Thundercloud
String.tooltip: Decreases a monster’s Endurance by 3% for 20 seconds after a successful hit. Effect stacks three times, for a total decrease of 9%. Has a chance to stagger. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Crimson Cataract
String.tooltip: Increases skill damage by 20%, but reduces the AoE radius.

String.name: Gale
String.tooltip: Reduces the RE cost of [Wind Walk] by 10, and increases duration by 15%.

String.name: Gentle Breeze
String.tooltip: Increases Movement Speed of nearby allies by 80 for 12 seconds.

String.name: Gust
String.tooltip: Increases PvP damage by 20%, but you take 10% more PvP damage while in effect.

String.name: Velocity
String.tooltip: <font color = '#F9B600'>Focused Heal</font> automatically locks on to the nearest 2 allies within 15m. Can be used while moving.

String.name: Heal
String.tooltip: Applies healing effect to ally on successful skill hit. The target receives 120 HP every second for 5 seconds. Healing effect is affected by Recovery Rate.

String.name: Weakening Touch
String.tooltip: Damages up to 2 enemies within 15m radius without lock-on, and fires a bolt that reduces the effect of healing skills on the target by 15%. Can be used while moving. Doubles the skill's cooldown.

String.name: Heal
String.tooltip: Increases HP recovery by 50% but decreases skill damage by 50%.

String.name: Blessing
String.tooltip: Applies [Enhanced Devoted Favor] to caster.

String.name: Amplification
String.tooltip: Increases skill damage by 80%. Successfully hitting a target with <font color = '#F9B600'>Weakening Touch</font> effect doubles the effect. However, the HP Recovery and [Enhanced Devoted Favor] effects no longer apply to allies.

String.name: Velocity
String.tooltip: <font color = '#F9B600'>Titanic Favor</font> automatically locks on to the nearest 2 allies within 15m. Can be used while moving.

String.name: Amplified Healing
String.tooltip: Successful skill hit applies <font color = '#F9B600'>Amplified Healing</font> which increases healing skills affecting the target by 15% for 3 seconds.

String.name: Downfall
String.tooltip: Damages up to 2 enemies within 15m radius without lock-on, and fires a [Downfall Bomb] that reduces the target's skill damage by 7.5%. Can be used while moving. Doubles the skill's cooldown.

String.name: Heal
String.tooltip: Doubles the size of the orb, and increases its speed and range by 30%.

String.name: Chain
String.tooltip: Heals the caster and sends a healing orb to the nearest ally within 15m. After recovering HP for the ally, the orb flies to and heals up to 4 additional allies within 15m.

String.name: Amplification
String.tooltip: Increases skill damage by 100%. Successfully hitting a target with [Downfall Bomb] effect doubles <font color = '#F9B600'>Downfall</font>'s damage reduction effect. However, the HP Recovery effect no longer applies to allies.

String.name: Blade Fury
String.tooltip: After a successful attack on an enemy player, they take 10% more damage and lose 863 HP per sec for 9 seconds.

String.name: Incise
String.tooltip: After a successful attack on a monster, decreases target's Endurance by 9%, and all attacks are considered to be attacks from behind for 4 seconds. Recovers your HP by 3%.

String.name: Restrained
String.tooltip: Decreases the damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Smite</font> by 90%, but increases the damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Grim Strike</font> by 10%.

String.name: Weak Point
String.tooltip: Increases duration by 20% and the chance to crit by 5%.

String.name: Blackout
String.tooltip: You and 3 nearby allies receive a cloak effect for 4 seconds. Caster receives [Assassination: Shrouded Escape] effect.

String.name: Snare
String.tooltip: While effect is active, a successful hit decreases the target's Movement Speed by 20%. (Stacks up to 4 times.)

String.name: Weak Point
String.tooltip: Attacks on monsters are considered to be attacks from behind. Each hit reduces Endurance by 3%. Stacks up to 3 times. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Velocity
String.tooltip: Increases Willpower consumption by 5, but increases skill damage by 20%.

String.name: Defending Team
String.tooltip: Takes 30% less damage while casting. Target player takes 3% more damage on successful hit. (Stacks up to 3 times.)

String.name: Fire
String.tooltip: When <font color = '#F9B600'>Mana Missiles</font> is chained with <font color = '#F9B600'>Dashing Reload</font>, <font color = '#F9B600'>Modular Weapon System</font> fires missiles that deal 15% more damage.

String.name: Integration
String.tooltip: Increases projectile's speed by 30% and damage by 20% when using <font color = '#F9B600'>Arcane Barrage</font> while <font color = '#F9B600'>Modular Weapon System</font> is active. Explosion radius is reduced by 30%. When using Arcane Barrage during this effect, Arcane Splash's damage doubles for a short period.

String.name: Force Field
String.tooltip: Summoning <font color = '#F9B600'>Modular Weapon System</font> briefly activates a force field that decreases damage of incoming ranged attacks on allies within 6m by 15%.

String.name: Resonance
String.tooltip: A successful hit increases damage dealt by 2% for 10 seconds.

String.name: Weak Spot Thrust
String.tooltip: Obtain 100 additional Rage after a successful hit. Attacks from behind deal 20% more damage. When activated, reduces cooldown of Flying Kick by 0.5 seconds.

String.name: Ironfist
String.tooltip: Increases reflected damage by 60% after triggering Perfect Defense.

String.name: Irregular
String.tooltip: Decreases aggro by 60% and attacks from behind deal 45% more damage. Removes frontal defense, increased aggro, and body size effects. Cannot use <font color = '#F9B600'>Infuriate</font> while active. <font color = '#F9B600'>Internal Wounds</font> effect does not trigger when using <font color = '#F9B600'>Rhythmic Blows</font>.

String.name: Sensation of Power
String.tooltip: The window for triggering Perfect Defense increases by 0.2 seconds.

String.name: Asceticism
String.tooltip: Decreases Rage consumption per second by 50%, but also decreases Power and Crit Factor bonus by 50%.

String.name: Corrosion Bomb
String.tooltip: After a successful hit, throws a bomb that increases damage dealt by 0.1% for 15 seconds. Stacks up to 10 times.

String.name: Outbreak
String.tooltip: Increases damage of Impact Bomb by 200%.

String.name: Sticky Bomb
String.tooltip: Decreases Movement Speed by 100% for 4 seconds after a successful hit. Does not affect boss monsters.

String.name: Avalanche Spirit
String.tooltip: Generates an additional 500 Chi over 10 seconds and increases the skill damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Fire Avalanche</font> by 15%.

String.name: Burning Spirit
String.tooltip: Generates an additional 500 Chi over 10 seconds and increases the chance to crit of <font color = '#F9B600'>Burning Heart</font> by 10%.

String.name: Lightning Spirit
String.tooltip: Generates an additional 500 Chi over 10 seconds and increases the skill damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Quick Attack</font>, <font color = '#F9B600'>Double Cut</font>, <font color = '#F9B600'>Skyfall</font>, and <font color = '#F9B600'>Circle of Steel</font> by 10%.

String.name: Focus
String.tooltip: Increases the skill damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Titansbane</font> by 30% and generates 200 Ragnarok points on a successful hit, and 400 Ragnarok points on a second hit. Cancels [Arun's Wail] and [Shara's Scream] effects on allies.

String.name: Sheen
String.tooltip: Doubles the skill damage bonus of [Arun's Wail] and [Shara's Scream], but decreases the skill damage of <font color = '#F9B600'>Titansbane</font> by 80%.

String.name: Armor
String.tooltip: Resists knockdown and stagger while casting <font color = '#F9B600'>Titansbane</font>. In addition, [Arun's Wail] applies a 10% damage reduction effect, and [Shara's Scream] applies a further 15%.

String.name: Spirit of Iron
String.tooltip: Reduces damage taken by 50% while casting. A successful hit on a monster reduces its Endurance by 4.5%. Stacks up to 2 times. Does not stack with the healer’s reduced Endurance effect.

String.name: Velocity
String.tooltip: Speeds casting for the first two hits of <font color = '#F9B600'>Shining Crescent</font> by 15%. Generates an additional 25 Ragnarok points per hit.

String.name: Bleeding
String.tooltip: A successful hit on an enemy player applies a bleeding effect, which reduces the target's HP over time and increases damage taken by 9%.
